Kalaxion Invasion Guide EYES ONLY 

Encryption code AZ+3

REF (23/22) Division 66bd/Subsection Orientation Basic Primary Clause: Notable figures

*******************************************

Fourth Bureau Addendum

*******************************************

Suzy Jenkins is from a very old Broadcliffs family and granddaughter of Sylvia (old Ma) Jenkins, the matriarch of the Broadcliffs Coven. A disruptive student with a poor academic and disciplinary record to match.

She is suspected of dabbling in ‘natural physics’. She is distinctly unpopular with her fellow students but is known to associate with Reginald Pickles and Gavin Holden.
